properties.Name: ProductDefinition
properties.Description: The definition(s) written into an Insurance Product.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: InsuranceDefinitionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Definition Type.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description:
The period start date that the associated definition is written into the insurance product.

Additional coverage definitions etc. may be added over time and mailed to the customer as updates.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description:
The period end date that the associated definition is written into the insurance product.

Additional coverage definitions etc. may be added over time and mailed to the customer as updates.

Columns.Name: ProductDefinitionStatement
Columns.Description: The text of the actual definition written into the Product.
